&lt;P&gt;After 3 nights of wiping due to bugs we just cleared the entire ballroom/hallway area first and beat it easily with 52 standing at the end and only 8 or 9 mobs alive (5 orcs + spiders/Spinstress).&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;So I just suggest that anyone doing this event take the 10 extra minutes to clear the entire area around this event to be safe.&lt;/P&gt;</description>
